is not suffused with politics?

21:17.276 --> 21:23.015 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
PETER ZEIDENBERG: Well, they --
that really
has been my experience when I
was in the public

21:23.048 --> 21:24.817 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
integrity section.

21:24.850 --> 21:30.756 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And I believe that still to be
the case that
the career prosecutors are not
political.

21:30.789 --> 21:37.229 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And, you know, unfortunately,
this has gotten
pulled into that, and I think it
will raise

21:37.263 --> 21:40.900 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
questions in people's mind
that's unfair and
very unfortunate.

21:40.933 --> 21:44.236 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Peter Zeidenberg,
Daniel Richman,
we thank you both.

21:44.270 --> 21:46.505 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
DANIEL RICHMAN: Thank you.

21:46.539 --> 21:54.513 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Even before this
FBI news broke
last Friday, I wanted to go out
on the campaign

21:54.547 --> 21:59.685 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
trail myself on this
next-to-the-last weekend
before Election Day to see both
candidates

21:59.718 --> 22:02.354 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
up close, and talk directly to
voters.

22:02.388 --> 22:06.725 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I headed first to a Clinton
event in Daytona
Beach, Florida.

22:06.759 --> 22:12.531 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Twenty-four hours after FBI
Director Comey's
letter jolted the race for
president, these

22:12.565 --> 22:17.870 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Florida voters waiting to see
Hillary Clinton
said they were not deterred by
the news.

22:17.903 --> 22:19.271 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
It doesn't bother you?

22:19.305 --> 22:20.339 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
LISA PEREZ, Hillary Clinton
Supporter: No,
she has nothing to hide.

22:20.372 --> 22:23.676 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
If she had, she -- no, she
doesn't.

22:23.709 --> 22:25.544 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Do you want Trump as our
president?

22:25.578 --> 22:26.545 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
Really?

22:26.579 --> 22:28.347 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
I mean, think about it.

22:28.380 --> 22:30.115 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
You got to weigh the pros and
the cons.

22:30.149 --> 22:34.453 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: In fact, Lisa
Perez and her
friend Barbara Ballach sounded
protective

22:34.486 --> 22:35.821 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
