22:35.854 --> 22:38.691 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
BARBARA BALLACH, Hillary Clinton
Supporter:
She has nothing to hide.

22:38.724 --> 22:43.295 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
As soon as it gets exposed,
people can put
it to rest.

22:43.329 --> 22:44.563 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
I'm not worried about her
e-mails.

22:44.597 --> 22:47.967 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
I'm more worried about the
issues.

22:48.000 --> 22:50.069 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Like what?

22:50.102 --> 22:51.070 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
For example, what?

22:51.103 --> 22:52.071 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
What issues?

22:52.104 --> 22:53.872 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
BARBARA BALLACH: Our economy.

22:53.906 --> 23:00.746 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
I feel real strong about
immigration, and
what Trump is threatening to do.

23:00.779 --> 23:01.947 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
