23:01.981 --> 23:05.184 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
He's going to ship people home
and break up
families.

23:05.217 --> 23:07.086 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
He's going to shame the Statue
of Liberty.

23:07.119 --> 23:08.087 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
LISA PEREZ: Right.

23:08.120 --> 23:09.088 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
He's going to bring us down.

23:09.121 --> 23:10.823 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
He's going to make this economy
worse.

23:10.856 --> 23:13.259 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
He is going to divide us.

23:13.292 --> 23:16.996 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Charles Ferguson
is a registered
Republican.

23:17.029 --> 23:18.564 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Did you consider Donald Trump?

23:18.597 --> 23:21.967 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
CHARLES FERGUSON, Hillary
Clinton Supporter:
Absolutely not.

23:22.001 --> 23:26.105 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I think Donald Trump would be a
disaster for
this country.

23:26.138 --> 23:33.912 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I really think that it would be
absolute chaos,
and it would be -- he would be
-- he would

23:33.946 --> 23:38.384 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
make our country his piggy bank,
and he'd
be the chief pig.

23:38.417 --> 23:42.554 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: When Clinton
arrived to speak,
she raised the FBI's move.

23:42.588 --> 23:45.991 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HILLARY RODHAM CLINTON (D),
Presidential Candidate:
It's pretty strange to put
something like

23:46.025 --> 23:51.063 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
