24:02.808 --> 24:04.843 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And why are you
and Samuel
here?

24:04.877 --> 24:06.645 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MARLO DUFFY: Because I want to
hear our future
president speak.

24:06.679 --> 24:08.881 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
This is historical, the first
woman president.

24:08.914 --> 24:13.585 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: To make that
happen, the campaign
is counting on canvassers,
supporters who

