with voters who
need a nudge to get to the
polls.

24:18.190 --> 24:21.694 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HILLARY RODHAM CLINTON: We just
reached a
milestone.

24:21.727 --> 24:26.932 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
More than 200 million Americans
are registered
to vote.

24:26.965 --> 24:28.734 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
