young people.

24:28.767 --> 24:30.202 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
(CHEERING AND APPLAUSE)

24:30.235 --> 24:33.872 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Including the
three Woody sisters.

24:33.906 --> 24:36.375 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
