Carlos, rounded out the picture.

25:05.104 --> 25:08.140 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DEBRA WOODY, Hillary Clinton
Supporter: I
feel that Hillary is going to be
the answer

25:08.173 --> 25:11.643 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
for not only my girls, but all
young women
and our entire country.

25:11.677 --> 25:13.679 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
CARLOS WOODY, Hillary Clinton
Supporter: Mr.
Trump is very volatile.

25:13.712 --> 25:15.814 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
