Republican.

25:19.118 --> 25:21.587 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: did you mean to
compare Donald
Trump to Satan?

25:21.620 --> 25:27.292 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CARLOS WOODY: I think, when you
