America.

26:28.320 --> 26:31.523 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
We need our children to have
jobs when they
get out of college.

26:31.557 --> 26:36.695 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Several Trump
fans told us
