in Chicago.

26:50.976 --> 26:53.278 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
When you say baggage, what are
you referring
to?

26:53.312 --> 26:58.417 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
RICHARD JARRETT: Well, I mean,
the -- he won't
release his tax returns.

26:58.450 --> 27:01.520 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
There's questions about the
women who came
out against him.

27:01.553 --> 27:07.059 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
