27:08.927 --> 27:12.331 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But I think all of that is still
better than
what the Clinton crime family
has to offer.

27:12.364 --> 27:17.503 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Rebecca Burr,
another Democrat
who supported Bernie Sanders in
the Nevada

27:17.536 --> 27:20.973 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
