uniform.

27:21.006 --> 27:24.343 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
"U.S. Department of Justice
inmate Hillary
Rodham Clinton."

27:24.376 --> 27:26.712 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
REBECCA BURR, Donald Trump
Supporter: I'm
looking at the bigger picture
here.

27:26.745 --> 27:28.814 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
