doesn't rig an
election.

27:28.847 --> 27:33.685 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I am looking for someone who
doesn't take
money from foreign interests
from overseas.

27:33.719 --> 27:38.891 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
