27:40.726 --> 27:43.028 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: What was your
reaction when
the story came out about Mr.
Trump's comments

27:43.061 --> 27:45.030 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
