tape?

27:45.063 --> 27:50.135 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
REBECCA BURR: I thought was that
that was
something that Hillary knew all
along.

27:50.168 --> 27:54.740 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I know that she has a lot of
tricks up her
sleeves.

27:54.773 --> 27:57.042 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And I wouldn't be surprised if
she has more
dirt on him.

27:57.075 --> 27:59.144 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
But as far as, does it offend me
as a woman?

27:59.177 --> 28:00.879 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
No.

28:00.913 --> 28:04.550 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DONALD TRUMP: As your president,
I will go
into the poorest communities and
work on a

28:04.583 --> 28:07.452 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
