revitalization.

28:07.486 --> 28:10.422 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
We will break decades of
failure.

28:10.455 --> 28:15.060 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Failures that
Arizonan James
Barber says he knows firsthand.

28:15.093 --> 28:19.698 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JAMES BARBER, Donald Trump
Supporter: I want
him to go into the inner cities
and fix them.

28:19.731 --> 28:22.067 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
It has not gotten better in the
50 years.

28:22.100 --> 28:25.704 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So, hopefully, he will bring a
much-needed
change.

28:25.737 --> 28:28.774 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And with that, we
